e being advised to consider two wheels where possible.\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999177869260597, \"rank\": 7.302713475233763e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A new report\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"more people\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 490}, {\"ngram\": \"bike\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 505}, {\"ngram\": \"car\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"two wheels\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 60 kilometers of bike paths will link the Games venues and 10,000 bike-rack spaces will be added to existing ones.\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More than 60 kilometers\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"bike paths\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games venues\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"10,000 bike-rack spaces\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"existing ones\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Metro and buses are also an option, but some metro stations near Olympic venues will be closed - meaning that hopping on a bike should be one of the smoothest ways to get around during the Games.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"buses\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"an option\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"some metro stations\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic venues\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"a bike\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 900}, {\"ngram\": 